Name: Happy New Year Clicker
About the game: New Year's clicker with New Year's achievements! There is no New Year's mood? Play the New Year's clicker! This game will be a good gift for you and your friends! Your goal is to buy all the gifts for the new year! Each gift hides behind itself a heap of achievements!                                                                Play, click, gift! Features: - Simple clicker; - New Year's music; - New Year's achievements; - Pleasant price; Happy New year and Merry Christmas!
